!data/raw/.gitkeep
!data/enriched/.gitkeep
!data/campaigns/sent/.gitkeep
!data/campaigns/replies/.gitkeep
!data/campaigns/conversions/.gitkeep

# Intake answers are user-specific — never commit (may contain secrets/PII)
intake/answers.md
intake/answers.*.md

